&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Position Summary&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Test Coordinator is responsible for planning, coordinating, and governing testing activities across the delivery lifecycle, with a strong emphasis on User Acceptance Testing (UAT). The role ensures business stakeholders are effectively supported to validate solutions, testing activities are aligned to the integrated programme plan, and risks, dependencies, and progress are clearly managed and reported.&amp;nbsp;The Test Coordinator operates between delivery teams and the business, providing structure, visibility, and control over testing activities. The role focuses on enabling business-led testing, ensuring upstream testing outcomes are understood, and confirming solutions are fit for purpose prior to release.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Understanding of Testing Activities Supporting UAT&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Test Coordinator understands the end-to-end testing activities required to enable effective User Acceptance Testing (UAT) and ensures these activities are coordinated, visible, and aligned to business validation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Testing Scope and Readiness&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Understands overall testing scope, environments, roles, timelines, and entry and exit criteria to ensure UAT is planned realistically and aligned to the integrated programme plan.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;UAT Preparation Inputs&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Ensures business-focused test scenarios, test data, access, and supporting materials are in place so business users can execute UAT efficiently and with confidence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Upstream Testing Outcomes&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Reviews and interprets system and integration testing results to confirm UAT readiness, identify residual risks, and prevent UAT being impacted by unresolved technical issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;UAT Coordination and Execution&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Plans and coordinates UAT activities, supports business testers, tracks execution progress, and ensures issues and blockers are managed promptly.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Results, Risks, and Sign-off&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Consolidates UAT outcomes, defects, and risks to support informed business sign-off and release readiness decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
